quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,46,"Mazima twatuma Musa n’obubonero bwaffe nti genda eri Falawo na bakungu be, olwo nno nabagamba nti mazima nze ndi mubaka w'omulabirizi w’ebitonde"
  43,47,Wabula bwe yabajjira n’obubonero bwaffe wagenda okulaba nga babusekerera
  43,48,Tetwabalaga kabonero konna okugyako nga kko kaba kanene okusinga kannaako (wabula era tebakkiriza) netubatusaako ebibonerezo oba olyawo ne bekyusa (okuva ku kye babaddeko)
  43,49,(Bwe balaba ebibonerezo) olwo nno ne bagamba nti owange ggwe omulogo tusabire Mukama omulabirizi wo ng’okozesa ebyo bye yakuwa (ebisabisibwa) mazima ffe ddala tujja kulungama
  43,50,Bwe twabagyako ebibonerezo amangu ago bo ne bamenya endagaano
  43,51,"Era Firawo nalangirira mu bantu be naagamba nti abange bantu bange obufuzi bwa Misiri si bwange, nga nagino emigga gikulukutira wansi wange abaffe temulaba"
  43,52,"Wabula nze nsinga ono (Musa) oyo yye anyomwa, era nga kumpi tasobola na kunnyonnyola (nsonga) yonna"
  43,53,Singa yanaanikibwa ebikomo ebya zaabu oba ba Malayika nebajja naye nga ba muwerekera (olwo nno) twanditegedde nti mubaka wa Katonda
  43,54,"(Firawo) bwatyo bwe yazannyira ku bwongo bwa bantu be, olwo nno ne bamugondera era mazima bo nebaba abantu abonoonyi"
  43,55,Bwe bamala okutunyiiza twababonereza ne tubazikiriza n’amazzi bonna
  43,56,Ne tubafuula abedda abogerwako era ne tubafuula eky'okulabirako eri ab'oluvanyuma